data.description: Motivated Seller!  Country roads take me home to this welcoming split level on a picturesque landscaped lot.  This home has so much to offer with a nice size living room w/ a propane fireplace to cozy up to on chilly nights, dining room and updated kitchen with SS appliances all remaining with the sale.  Three comfortable bedrooms including a master suite w/private bath.  Lower level family room w/ a walkout patio door is great recreation space or would also be perfect for an in-law quarters.  Attached garage w/electric opener and a detached carport.  Keeping warm will be economical with the propane furnace and hotwater heater.  The rear deck is the perfect summertime spot to enjoy a morning cup of coffee.  Let's not forget the location only minutes to outdoor adventures at Blue Mountain Ski Area and Beltzville Lake.  Only a short drive to PA Turnpike or Routes 209, 115 and 33 making it an easy commute!
